                "invention-title": [
                    "Iron-making process for reforming and heating natural gas/coke oven gas in hot blast stove",
                    "一种天然气/焦炉煤气在热风炉重整加热的炼铁工艺"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides an ironmaking process for reforming and heating natural gas/coke oven gas in a hot-blast stove. The ironmaking process comprises the following steps: arranging a catalyst at the middle lower part of a hot-blast stove body; blast furnace top gas without CO2 removal and combustion-supporting air are introduced from the top of the hot blast stove to burn the hot blast stove; the method comprises the following steps: blowing mixed gas of natural gas or coke oven gas and partial CO2-removed blast furnace top gas from the bottom of a hot blast stove, and performing medium-temperature reforming and high-temperature heating from bottom to top to obtain high-temperature hydrogen-rich reducing gas; and the high-temperature hydrogen-rich reducing gas is used for shaft furnace direct reduction ironmaking or blast furnace hydrogen-rich ironmaking. The ironmaking process for reforming and heating the natural gas/coke oven gas in the hot blast stove, provided by the invention, is energy-saving, efficient, relatively low in cost and simple in process."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种天然气/焦炉煤气在热风炉重整加热的炼铁工艺，其步骤包括：在热风炉炉身中下部设置催化剂；从热风炉顶部通入未脱除CO2高炉炉顶煤气和助燃空气对热风炉烧炉；将天然气或焦炉煤气与部分脱除CO2高炉炉顶煤气的混合气体从热风炉底部吹入，自下而上经中温重整，高温加热得到高温富氢还原气体；将高温富氢还原气体用于竖炉直接还原炼铁或高炉富氢炼铁。本发明提供的一种天然气/焦炉煤气在热风炉重整加热的炼铁工艺，节能高效、成本较低、工艺简单。"
                }
            ]
